text:

Oh, god. Sorry, I have so much goddamned dust in my eyes right now. Geez, it is dusty in here. Can we do something about this? These tears streaming down my face are from the dust. 
Since the fire, Nalu is reportedly doing okay. She spent a day in an animal hospital and is back living with her loving owner, Crystal Lamirande, who can be seen comforting Nalu in the video as well. 
No people were hurt in the fire, which took 23 firefighters to get under control. Thanks to them, no dogs were hurt, either.
